original_title: Papunta Ka Pa Lang, Pabalik Na Ako
overview: This star-studded movie explicits the popular Filipino saying, ""Papunta ka pa lang, pabalik na ako"". Eddie Garcia, Joko Diaz, Gloria Diaz, Jennifer Sevilla and Glydel Mercado complete the cast of this 1997 movie.
title: Papunta Ka Pa Lang, Pabalik Na Ako
